01:41:40.677 --> 01:41:42.136
Shame on you!

01:41:45.015 --> 01:41:47.725
Ah! The former Miss Levy.

01:41:51.355 --> 01:41:53.022
Shall we, my dear?

01:42:02.032 --> 01:42:04.117
- Good night.
- God bless you, Charlie.

01:42:05.869 --> 01:42:08.579
- Uh, I'll call you.
