01:42:17.714 --> 01:42:19.674
Hey, let's go on.

01:42:20.300 --> 01:42:22.552
Not tonight, old darling. A bit tired.

01:42:24.054 --> 01:42:27.348
It's funny, you know, you look a lot like him.

01:42:29.143 --> 01:42:30.643
