to make me a talkie. Now I'm making a talkie.

01:45:21.857 --> 01:45:24.358
Yeah, but not this.

01:45:28.572 --> 01:45:30.197
I know this man.

01:45:31.199 --> 01:45:34.285
We're born the same year, four days apart.

01:45:35.579 --> 01:45:37.621
