until you played

01:50:37.881 --> 01:50:41.175
right into his hands by shutting Joan out.

01:50:45.639 --> 01:50:47.097
You're improving, Frank.

01:50:47.182 --> 01:50:50.142
Can't you find someone else
to play with?

01:50:50.226 --> 01:50:53.062
